&lt;p&gt;Queste bimbe di due anni corrono &lt;em&gt;sempre&lt;/em&gt;:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/aadm/15705805161" title="20141102_AA25759 by Alessandro Amato, on Flickr"&gt;&lt;img src="https://farm9.staticflickr.com/8276/15705805161_ced9390ec7_c.jpg" width="800" height="534" alt="20141102_AA25759"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;


